of non-Gibbsian phenomena related to cooling, albeit in a mean-field\nsetup.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 May 2010 09:50:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Sep 2010 12:59:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
